            "question": "Any installation tips for first‑timers?",
            "answer": "<p>Plan the mounting location, verify roof thickness or bracket strength, route wiring away from sharp edges and heat, and use a properly fused circuit as specified in the manual. If you’re unsure, a professional install ensures a reliable, code‑compliant setup.</p>",
